Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.33,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,为什么你要投降
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:07.73,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.26,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你不战斗的话 我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:42.38,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.17,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,命运不也让我们连在一起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.05,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,快走啊 不要管我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:52.06,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大家 地球就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:14.41,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}被外星人捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.26,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,虽然我们从即将爆炸的苏联舰中逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:25.10,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,但是 想到牺牲自己让我们逃出来的丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.84,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,一切都只能祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.30,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他们追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.39,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,等一下 我出击就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.50,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.93,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,刚刚逃出来的时候贝布鲁和布鲁迪的能源已用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.06,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,能动的只剩下我的雷兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.15,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.75,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,总之我会全力以赴 剩下的拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:48.91,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.47,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.30,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没有能源的意思是说这航天飞机不能发射武器咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:58.82,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:02:59.62,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.78,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,说不定我们逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.74,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,那航天飞机的能源应该快用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.86,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,可以推测太空船503的可动率吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:17.99,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.19,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已经消耗98%以上的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.91,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,能量剩余量已到了极限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:24.53,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.11,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,还有三十秒就能跟他们接触
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:37.93,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,全员排开队形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:40.79,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.79,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,今天一定要分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:48.46,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.63,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,少尉 等一下 先不要攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.94,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,就这点本事打得赢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:12.80,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.67,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,好 这就是你的末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:30.51,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.04,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.60,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,没听到我叫你不要攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.43,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.35,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,全员去包围航天飞机 照队形待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们被包围了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:01.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.39,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,英二 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.92,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:06.79,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:07.99,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:08.68,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.24,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,英二 我就直接说了 你投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.33,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,我知道你们的太空船已经没有能源了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.23,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,不要再做无谓的反抗了 快投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.34,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,谁会投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.84,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们才不会听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.30,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,闭嘴 我在跟英二说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.62,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.46,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,现在我们枪口下的不是只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.21,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,前辈 请答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.11,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要对太空船里的地球人下手 请答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.17,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,不用担心 我会妥善处置的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.47,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了 我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.72,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,好 回航天飞机去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.35,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.05,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你为什么投降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.14,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我们就快能看到地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.75,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你不战斗的话 我上 走开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.25,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,在这里要听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.39,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.88,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.45,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.42,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,人生有时也要举白旗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:03.08,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不过那白旗 只是为了要反抗的一种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.55,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那是 莎 莎 莎士比亚说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.47,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不是 是我爹经常说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.27,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,每次我输给对手时他都会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:23.10,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是这样啊 可是现在的情况正好一样不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.45,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,现在不投降的话 大家就无法得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.03,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,其实大卫也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.96,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,虽然知道这道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:42.14,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,但好不容易逃到这 要投降真的很令人难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.77,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,还差一点就到地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.50,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.04,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你说没有让他们活下去的必要是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.03,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,是的 陛下下令要把那些残存的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.55,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,和反叛者全都消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.80,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,把他们当俘虏也就等于把他们都消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.00,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,没必要杀没有反抗意识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.24,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,陛下的话里还有这一层意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.79,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.24,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.69,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,不 我想要不要再询问陛下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.57,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你觉得他们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.79,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,就是叛徒跟地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:35.47,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,只有这样而已吗 我觉得他们跟我们一样都是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.76,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.84,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我不懂您的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.77,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,算了 这里拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:41.85,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.16,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.24,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,你留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.46,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,中尉 人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.30,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.31,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你变壮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.48,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.15,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你怎么了 先坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.06,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,怎么变得这么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.52,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是俘虏 怎么能嬉皮笑脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.84,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,好讽刺啊 没想到我们彼此之间还会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.70,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不过我真的吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:32.53,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,虽然现在才意识到 但外星人竟长得跟我们一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.47,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,因为进化的过程一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.02,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,说不定是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.92,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不过我们会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.19,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,现在不是为了反击才一时投降的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.57,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,所以我们要快想反击的方法对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.77,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.14,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你的爸爸被要求对背叛负责而被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.42,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你的妈妈和玖丽亚现在已经被软禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.99,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你好冷静 你已有这种觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是的 我早就料到会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:05.98,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:09.05,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,为什么要这样包庇地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.53,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,虽说你体内有一半地球人的血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.02,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,但你不是在古拉多斯长大的的古拉多斯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:19.99,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,地球 对我来说和古拉多斯一样都是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.14,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还有几亿地球人生活在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.16,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,你有看到他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.67,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们跟我们一样也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.78,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们也以自己的星球为荣而一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.68,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.68,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我爱着蔚蓝又美丽的地球 就像爱着古拉多斯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.11,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,蔚蓝而美丽 你有看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.59,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不用看也知道 我听爸爸说了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那景象已真实地烙在我心里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:51.28,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,如果照你所说人类以自己的美丽的地球为荣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.46,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,那为什么还要彼此征服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那是他们目前的组织有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.28,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,人民并不想要战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.18,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.35,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,是跟你在一起的那些人说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.16,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:10.44,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,我们只想改变目前人类的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.11,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,并没有要毁灭地球的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,古拉多斯明明就想让地球爆发末日战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.89,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,如果真的爆发的话 地球上的大自然和环境全都会被破坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:26.53,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,不这样的话 现在的地球是不可能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:32.86,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,这是古拉多斯的中央电脑经过长时间计算得出的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.32,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那个计算结果大错特错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.46,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.84,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,那食物要运到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.09,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,俘虏那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.03,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,什么 是谁的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.13,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,是盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.11,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:57.45,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,他还是想让他们活下去是吗 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.32,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,猫粮都比这好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:13.47,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他去好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.78,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你说英二吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.82,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没错 他该不会被怎么样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.17,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不要讲这种不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.06,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.35,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.40,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对啊 他的食物也被送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:25.49,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.40,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他们有没有对你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.62,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.58,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们没对我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:34.58,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.05,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,这有食物 虽然不太好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.66,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.99,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,为了身体还是吃一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.62,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,切 刚才明明就说那东西像猫粮似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:49.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.80,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,怎么了 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.10,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我想到怎么逃出去的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.00,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.40,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你的意思是说我想不出方法是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:13:59.78,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,看你还蛮自信的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.15,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我知道 我会照你的命令做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.64,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,可是为什么是你来报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.26,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:13.31,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉他因为在忙着审问俘虏 所以我替他报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.27,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,在处理俘虏方面 中尉和副官您的意思一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.60,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,是祖鲁副官吗 少尉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.22,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我现在替您报告俘虏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.50,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,替我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.22,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉 你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.68,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,是 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.90,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,关于处理俘虏的方法我刚才听少尉说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.93,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,就在你那里处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.32,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,处理的意思是指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.16,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,处死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.05,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你说是说处死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.40,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,怎么了 你不也想这么做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.95,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,这是古雷斯科陛下的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:49.11,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,当然 要照作战计划进行 俘虏的事没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:53.12,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,可是这些俘虏里大都是非战斗人员的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.65,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,所以怎样 你对古雷斯科陛下的命令有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:03.10,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,还是跟叛徒一家的关系 让你又心软了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.92,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,不 我没这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:05.85,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.62,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,之所以会把追击队交给你 就是要试试你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:14.01,Default_Sub,Zool,0,0,0,,总之 把俘虏处死 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.32,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.26,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我没别的意思 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.76,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我只是看中尉你太忙了 所以才帮你报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.48,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你也赞成把他们处死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:33.30,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我不敢有个人的意思 我只是听命行事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.08,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉你不会无视陛下的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.24,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,这样的话 连中尉你都会被当叛徒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.18,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,所以请你下达处刑的命令吧 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.20,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.57,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.37,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.53,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,开门 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.49,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我的同伴很难受 帮忙想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.68,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你们看 他肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.54,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好痛 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.65,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,等一下 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.27,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我的同伴这么难受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.93,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你们难道这么无动于衷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶 至少给个药嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.83,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.73,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.19,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,什么一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.09,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.39,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,这样一定不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:38.18,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好奇怪 电视上这样都会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.07,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,结果害我们空欢喜一场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.14,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,对啊 还害我想说一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.16,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,没办法 一定还有别的机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:56.11,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,玖丽亚 如果你失去弟弟了 你还会原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.27,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,打开 把他们带走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:08.99,Default_Sub,Soldiers,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.93,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,都给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.57,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.86,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.10,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要带我们去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.56,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,一个很远的地方 去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:21.98,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.70,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,所有人都给我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:39.78,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,英二 这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:40.69,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是密闭室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:41.99,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,密闭室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.36,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你要把我们运到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.50,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不会要把我们丢到太空中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.40,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你想杀了我们是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.10,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,不要啰嗦了 快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.90,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是盖尔中尉的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.09,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,不是中尉 是古雷斯科陛下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.70,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.56,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么能让你们就这样把我们丢到太空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.71,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要杀就在这杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.23,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,你给我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.76,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,要杀就在这杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:08.55,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:17.22,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,我们的船不想被你们地球人的血玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.14,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.60,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,是你下不了手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.61,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,这样的话 我就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.98,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,快住手 你想杀了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.41,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:56.47,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.89,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,把枪丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:02.69,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,没事的 他不敢动手 快射死他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.19,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,把枪丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.44,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,大家 到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.41,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不要一直抓着枪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.08,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,站在那里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.99,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.96,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,什么 你说他们要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.51,Default_Sub,Solider,0,0,0,,找到了 在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.21,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快去航天飞机那 去补充能源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:49.52,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.07,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.15,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.22,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,把我也杀了吧 这样叛徒就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.92,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,大家把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.91,Default_Sub,Callea,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:14.15,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,英二 我一直不对你下手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.74,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,并不是因为我爱你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.47,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,是因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:23.94,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,我只是相信我应该能开辟一条道路 救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.99,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,对不起 可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.99,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你想说你不会改变心意是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:29.85,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.96,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不管前辈你怎么说我都要去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.04,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,那是我背负的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.24,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.17,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.16,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.39,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,给我帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.11,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,丢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:00.54,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.18,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.47,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,也许你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.61,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,回舰桥 全员戒备待命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:14.11,Default_Sub,Soldier,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 这边也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:21.01,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:21.46,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:26.26,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.24,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二 不捉她当人质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.16,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我们要拿她来争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.62,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:33.41,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.77,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,把卡露拉少尉回收 并追击地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:01.85,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,英二 我们之间的关系已经完全破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.26,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,都完了 你还想演到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.67,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不 这次我的肚子 真的 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.73,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,弄假成真是吗 你一定太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:23.29,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,哦 拿着枪到处乱射的你也有纤细的一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.10,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:25.93,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.35,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我们又幸运的活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:40.10,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,可英二的脸上却浮现出异样的苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:48.78,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,就是他跟那个叫前辈的人 两人切不断的深厚情谊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:56.84,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,我知道你一定不会原谅手上沾满你弟弟鲜血的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.38,Default_Sub,Gale,0,0,0,,再见了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.25,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,再见了 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:08.57,Layzner_Title,David,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(720,790)}变成苍之流星
